{"type": "article", "id": 28871, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-06-29T06:59:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 29540, "name": "kukka"}, {"id": 29541, "name": "Levantin Design"}, {"id": 29542, "name": "Openmint"}, {"id": 29543, "name": "Ludwig Rensch"}, {"id": 29544, "name": "Sergey Levantin"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703121522CyWLD4IkENVvXjPq.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">          </p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Seamless by Aaron Mazikowski &amp; Sean Naderzad</h2>\n<p>越来越多的办公场所采用了开放式的设计，虽然大大增加了自由度，但随之而来的却是维持注意力的问题，一些常见的干扰可能来自路过的同事或者是手边的电子设备。圣何塞州立大学的两位学生 Aaron Mazikowski 和 Sean Naderzad 设计了一款名为 Seamless 的办公桌，圆弧形的无缝结构参考了摄影棚里的白色幕布，创造出半封闭式的个人空间，阻隔了一部分视线，但又不会带给人一种被笼罩的感觉。Seamless 配置了两层木制隔板，可以放下各类办公用品。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide medium-insert-active\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031223451Xt5nWgOQKYpjqm0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122346VJ2KqaFTZrtiXAg3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122346Bb862yM4SUusjZHq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031223475bwrVP0SAFjNJdkE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122347lfsCpcjBXA3oHLGq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 30px; text-align: left; background-color: transparent;\">Paper by Ludwig Rensch</span></h2>\n<p>作为常用的办公设备，打印机千篇一律的造型是不是已经让你感到乏味，好像进入了一间没有美感的打印室？今天我们要介绍的 <a href=\"http://www.ludwigrensch.com/paper-a-printer-you-actually-want\">Paper</a> 是德国设计师 <a href=\"http://www.ludwigrensch.com/\">Ludwig Rensch</a> 的作品，他的初衷是打造一款功能齐全而且不影响室内环境的打印机。Rensch 用按钮和信号灯替代了常见的触摸式显示屏，即使需要手动操作也很容易上手。它同时具有打印、扫描和复印三种功能，通过专门的应用和网页传输资料。橙色机身更是为沉闷的办公环境注入了一股温暖活泼的感觉。它目前还是一款概念产品，尚未投入生产。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122347ZIGJjUoa7Vlv1TdQ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122348ZDOH9vCAl1PrViUp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.599022\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122348wYdGVS4ltcQi02RW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.599022\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122349rd8FWeCvls3aN1pz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.599022\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122350xFkGU9rQDJTfItCP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.599022\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122350e0WMobu3j8ISmgGQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.599022\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Ridges by kukka</h2>\n<p>如果你有用搁板收纳小物的习惯，不妨看看英国工作室 <a href=\"http://www.kukkastudio.co.uk/\">kukka</a> 推出的这套 Ridges 金属搁板。每一块都经过激光切割并且折叠成了简单的几何形状，搭配上鲜亮的颜色就好像是在墙上建立了一个特别的小空间。你可以通过三角形的缺口摆上小物，或者利用金属磁性悬挂一些装饰品。这是它的<a href=\"http://kukka.co.uk/collections/home/products/ridges\">购买链接</a>，售价为 280 英镑，每一块搁板还附带一个浅盘。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122350GZxV8AYzRpLlkfvu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122351n0r5HDkiA1dNPpXs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122351QJwM86fY3idkIevE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031223517CUxi4E1ZyQAkWfT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122352932QoHcJnqE4zBFM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122352WZ80RT1QmuAo4fab.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>FITMENTS by Levantin Design</h2>\n<p>乌克兰设计师 <a href=\"http://levantindesign.com/\">Sergey Levantin</a> 的作品大多由纤细的几何线条构成。FITMENTS 是他最新设计的一款落地灯，灯泡和电线直接被金属框架所包围，看起来既简洁又大方。由于摒弃了传统的灯罩和灯柱，FITMENTS 带给人一种轻盈的感觉，适合放在空间较小的环境当中。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122353DOoPsJpHS9ZNURkh.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122353u0IAnqPrflhvGJw4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122354oJshz4adg8NyV6YA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122356vVgQcuHWta69AYTS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031223568yQJdOurnml7DkIx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Touch of Bass by Case of Bass</h2>\n<p>可以听的照片不再是天方夜谭了：当你第一眼看到 Touch of Bass 系列并且听到音乐时可能还会纳闷音源来自何方。实际上，这些由 <a href=\"http://www.caseofbass.com/\">Case of Bass</a> 设计的产品本身就是一个精致的音响设备。机身隐藏在相片背后的暗盒中，真实的喇叭则穿过相片中预留的空缺处，最外面则是固定用的相框——远远看上去就是一幅栩栩如生的摄影作品，只有靠近了从侧面观察才能惊喜地发现那些隐藏的细节。Touch of Bass 的高颜值和实用性让它不管放置在什么环境下都会让人眼前一亮，你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/368403916/a-touch-of-bass-the-sound-system-for-the-aesthetic\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 99 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122356JwGTN7zd63iuWqQE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031223572MFPWkrmYjL0xqVe.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63043478\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122358sNM1o3crLuUTB7tD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122359yQ74hMNZiYAF90pr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122359XfzcrpbqDMPvgnV3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122359OfFjyPBaEr35oS6n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Single Estate by Openmint</h2>\n<p>Jaf Tea 委托 <a href=\"http://openmintdesign.com/\">Openmint</a> 为旗下的精选锡兰红茶系列 Single Estate 设计了一套全新的包装。由于这一系列的茶叶都经过专业茶人的挑选，Openmint 的设计师们在包装上加入了很多向斯里兰卡传统茶叶生产致敬的元素：等级、评价、口感、浓度以及出产区域都在铁盒上有所标注，带给人一种统一而且复古的感觉。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031224004jLMoSkUlIfeOxYh.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62533333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122400qaQbtM0wLgvkKpYI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62533333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122401IylBn6PEtVT89Ypu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61866667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122401MviTCbK9jGBc4n8f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62533333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031224027wnYldfm8SGUIc5s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122402RQd8P27a3YobzTXW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62533333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}